50|$|Idaho Legislative District 22 {{is one of}} 35 {{districts of}} the Idaho Legislature. It is {{currently}} represented by Lori Den Hartog, Republican <b>of</b> <b>Meridian,</b> John Vander Woude, Republican <b>of</b> <b>Meridian,</b> and Jason Monks, Republican <b>of</b> <b>Meridian.</b>|$|R
